  %p
    Because you finished on the first-place team in the #{@div.name} Division, you could be eligible for a scholarship and
    consideration for an internship at MITRE or an industry partner.  Please email
    #{link_to 'ctf@mitre.org', 'mailto:ctf@mitre.org'} with your official
    college, university, or high school transcript AND an up-to-date resume to verify your eligibility.
    Both a transcript and a resume are required for the award of any scholarship prize.
- elsif @rank <= 10
  %p
    Because you finished in the top ten, we are requesting your resume and transcript. If youâ€™re interested, please
    email #{link_to 'ctf@mitre.org', 'mailto:ctf@mitre.org'} with your official college, university, or high school
    transcript AND an up-to-date resume.
- if @rank <= 10
  %p
    While this competition was open to professional and government participants as part of cyber training, only
